 * Enter where economy reformed: india
Enter the currency: $
Enter the value: 1.5
Enter year: 2020
As economic reforms picked up the pace,india GDP grew five-fold to reach US$1.5 trillion in 2020 (as per IMF estimates).
 */
 */
